  "title": "Talent Acquisition Manager (Healthcare) #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: Up to $7K <br /><br /><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Lead and manage a team of 8, providing guidance, mentorship, and performance management.</li><li>Co develop and implement strategic talent acquisition plans to meet the organization's hiring needs.</li><li>Ensure operational excellence in all recruitment processes and procedures.</li><li>Stay abreast of industry trends and best practices in talent acquisition, continuously improving our recruitment strategies.</li><li>Analyze recruitment metrics and provide regular reports to senior management.</li><li>Foster relationships with stakeholders (internal and external) including hiring managers, agencies, educational institutes, etc.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in any field </li><li>Min. 4-5 years relevant experience in TA/ Recruitment </li><li>Able to handle high volume of recruitment </li></ul><p><br />For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg<br />All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence<br />Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)<br />R2197564<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br />99C4599</p>",
